CLAN: Secretive organizations of Rifts Earth

Syntax: clan
        clan join <name>

DESCRIPTION:
  Clans are powerful, secretive organizations operating on Rifts Earth.
  Joining a clan may change your OCC, grant special abilities, or unlock
  tattoo slots unavailable to ordinary characters.

  Clan membership is permanent. Choose carefully.

COMMANDS:
  clan
      Displays your current clan membership.

  clan join <name>
      Attempts to join a named clan. Most clans require you to have
      discovered enough information about them before the name is
      recognized. Seek clues in the world.

AERIHMAN:
  A clan whose name must be spoken to be believed. Little is known
  publicly. Rumours speak of tattooed assassins, of shadow magic,
  and of an order predating the Rifts themselves.

  Those who find the truth and speak the name become Sunaj Assassin.

NOTES:
  - You may only belong to one clan.
  - Clan joining may alter your OCC, skills, and tattoo slots.
  - Some clans are only available to certain races or alignments.

SEE ALSO: touch, equipment, tattoo masters
